    "nom_orig": "Jun",
    "texte_orig": "After[SP]that...[1205][001E][SP]We[SP]only[SP]have[SP]to[SP]defeat[SP]Father.\n[E1][E2][E3]>[SP]There's[SP]an[SP]inscription[SP]in[SP]the[SP]relief.",
